- Okay. Okay. Okay.

11
00:00:45.171 --> 00:00:47.881
There's something about those dolls.

12
00:00:47.882 --> 00:00:49.091
I think I've seen them before.

13
00:00:55.765 --> 00:00:57.307
No! No!

14
00:00:57.308 --> 00:00:58.808
- We have to...
- Donna!

15
00:00:58.809 --> 00:00:59.685
